https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/41YW0QyM8q9eK8OHdOIRgy5GuoH.jpg Multi-platinum recording artists release their first-ever live DVD. Recorded in April 2005, the shows were filmed in the band's hometown of Atlanta during two special sold-out performances featuring the Atlanta Symphony Youth Orchestra. The 20-song collection spans ninety minutes and encompasses hits from Collective Soul's seven studio albums, including their latest release, "Youth". Collective Soul - Home
